<input type="tel" placeholder="901234567" value={"+998" + phone} onChange={(e) => {
            const val = e.target.value;
            if (val.startsWith("+998")) {
              setPhone(val.slice(5).replace(/\D/g, ''));
            } else {
              setPhone(val.replace(/\D/g, ''));
            }
          }} className={phoneError ? "error" : ""} required />
